self.title: CDISC SEND Pregnancy Findings Result Terminology

definition: Terminology relevant to the results for pregnancy findings.
name: Pregnancy Findings Result
preferredTerm: CDISC SEND Pregnancy Findings Result Terminology

terms.definition: Loss of all or part of the products of conception prior to the scheduled c-section date or expected delivery date.
A birth event that occurs prior to the scheduled c-section date or expected delivery date.
Observed to be negative for a pregnancy test or not pregnant.
Observed to be or have been pregnant or positive for a pregnancy test.
A pregnancy result for a female that had all intrauterine deaths.
A term referring to the lack of definitive criteria for classification of a finding.
